<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.10">
<l>cantoṭu kāraki luñcuman tutaṭaṅ kaḷporutu</l>
<l>vantiḻi yuñcilam pāṟuṭai māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>cuntara ṉaiccurum pārkuḻaṟ kōtai tokutturaitta</l>
<l>centamiḻ pattumval lārtiru mālaṭi cērvarkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those capable [of mastering] the ten [songs] in refined Tamil</l>
<l>that Kōtai—with locks where bees abide—gathered and spoke on</l>
<l>the Handsome Man, who stood in Māliruñcōlai with the Cilampu-river,</l>
<l rend="indent">—which, bearing eagle-wood along with sandalwood trees,</l>
<l>comes down, dashing against the shores—</l>
<l>will reach Tirumāl’s feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
